  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, straits are always the worst place to-- and we left behind the Russian railways, and we saw the Russian people in their dirty [RUSSIAN] they were called.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That is parkas there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The locomotive drivers, and his assistants, and the firemen, and so on, everybody dirty, and just sloppy, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we walked out in Japan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the first thing we saw on the railway yards, next to the shipping [INAUDIBLE], we saw a Japanese fellow in a light blue [INAUDIBLE] uniform with white gloves-- with white gloves-- with a-- with a basket on his back, and a long stick with a pointed iron nail, picking up every little piece of paper from the rails to make sure that there is no waste, or no-- nothing dirty, or nothing disorderly.",
      "word_count": 74
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we looked at the locomotive standing by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the people on the locomotive shoving the coal into the-- into the oven wore white gloves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you had the feeling of contrast of cultural-- and we are coming to-- we are coming to an Asian culture.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We are leaving European culture behind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we are coming to Asian culture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was the Asian culture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was February.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And those who had colds wore masks to protect the other people, not to give them their cold.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was the immediate encounter and comparison, that it was visual.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, yet, it was [INAUDIBLE] because it prompted you to think, and make comparisons about what you have just left, and what you just encountered that you never-- never imagined.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, the language was a jumble of noises that you couldn't make out, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
